7%85%E9%81%8A%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F-%E7%B1%B2%E5%8B%A4%E6%B4%97%E6%89%8B-%E6%9A%AB%E6%9C%AA%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E8%A1%8C%E7%A8%8B/</a><br />\n<br />\n美國疾控中心周三 (19日) 因應新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情對香港發出第一級旅遊注意，提醒前往當地的國民逼免與病人接觸，並要勤洗手。中心亦強調，現時並不建議國民取消或延遲前往香港的行程。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>美國疾控中心指出，香港已出現新型冠狀病毒肺炎個案，加上病毒可人傳人，提醒前往香港的美國國民需逼免與病人接觸，並要勤洗手。</strong>中心亦促請若過去 14 天曾到訪香港並出現發燒、咳嗽或呼吸困難等症狀，應向醫護人員尋求協助並報告最近的旅遊史。中心亦強調，現時並不建議國民取消或延遲前往香港的行程。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">現時疾控中心亦向中國發出第三級的旅遊警告，建議國民無非必要也不要前往中國旅遊。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"39e0197927cdad6818ae066850aeafacdbdca085","tid":1888274,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T06:08:53.000Z","msg":"2020年2月20日 下午12:17<br />\n政府特別上班安排 續實行至3月1日"},{"pid":"991706c2409d988419d18ef5e51bddba60536b86","tid":1888274,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T06:09:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oa7rtL7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foa7rtL7.jpg&h=d26137f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83936c731d7fb58a4d53ebaf856c7a8512412ab1","tid":1888274,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T06:13:45.000Z","msg":"新加坡呢"},{"pid":"19630c65f7985ab8bc9f8f16ca629b4b9a1d48ab","tid":1888274,"uid":263349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83936c731d7fb58a4d53ebaf856c7a8512412ab1","tid":1888274,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T06:13:45.000Z","msg":"新加坡呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T06:19:05.000Z","msg":"新加坡 唔係中國一部分<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"698c776c3a0f6093ebc485df9e81315c908314e5","tid":1888274,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T06:32:58.000Z","msg":"一巴巴打落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留名林鄭屌尻特朗普<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji